This paper deals with image editing using human-drawn sketches, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel deep learning framework, which involves training a neural network, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
